                    <h3>Distributed & JSON-ified widgets.</h3>
                    <p>Each and every <em>developer</em> in your organization can contribute to the dashboard. It's 
                    easy as returning JSON object over http!</p>
                    <p>Because <em>widget</em> is a simply JSON object, you can write your widgets in any language 
                    you want. The only limit is your imagination!</p>
                ]]></text>
