                    <h3>Out-Of-The-Box Functionalities.</h3>
                    <p>Hoborg Labs provide default set of widgets and tools for some commonly use software 
                    packages like git, redmine, jenkins, graphite, opsview or github.</p>
                    <p>We use {{ mustache }} JS templates and jQuery. We recommend 
                    <a href="http://www.rgraph.net/">RGraph</a> for simple js graphs and 
                    <a href="http://graphite.wikidot.com">Graphite</a> for more dynamic charts.
                    </p>
