                    Or check more options in 
                    <a href="/doc">documentation</a>.
                    </p>
                    <h3>DIY!</h3>
                    <p>If you want to integrate dashboard with your existing page, follow tese simple steps.</p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Download <a href="http://get.hoborglabs.com/dashboard/dashboard.phar">dashboard.phar</a> into vendors/ folder.</li>
                        <li>Download <a href="http://get.hoborglabs.com/dashboard/dashboard-assets.tgz">dashboard-assets.tgz</a> into vendors/ folder and unzip in subfolder of  your host public folder. For instance htdocs/dashboard</li>
                        <li>Create dashboard.php or download it <a href="https://gist.github.com/1512137">from here</a>.</li>
                    </ol>
